    "bio_summary": "Mujo, also known as Mujo情, is a Hungarian lo-fi beats producer currently residing in Hokkaido, Japan. His real name is Király Brúnó, also active under the alias Hanakoto Bang. His earliest release titled \"Buddah Killah vs. Mujo情\" was a collaboration with Buddah Killah and was released on September 25, 2010. Soon after, \"Mystagogue Beat Tape\" was dropped on November 11, 2010. It was followed by the release of \"Hwang Jang Lee - Korean Lo\" on May 29, 2011. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/mujo\">R",
